---
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Clara Cuartas" description="About Clara Cuartas - Designer and Educator">
  <div class="stack gap-20">
    <main class="wrapper about">
      <Hero title="About Me" />

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Hello! I am Clara Cuartas, a graphic designer with over ten years of experience in UI/UX. I enjoy creating
            digital experiences that are both functional and accessible. With a strong background in psychology and
            teaching, I have a unique perspective on understanding and addressing user needs empathetically. My goal is
            to design solutions that truly make a difference in people's lives.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Professional Experience</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Throughout my career, I have worked on designing interfaces for web and mobile devices, honing my UI and UX
            skills. My background in graphic design and constant updating on the latest UI/UX trends allow me to offer
            creative and effective solutions. I deeply appreciate teamwork and have led various projects, always aiming
            to create intuitive and accessible digital experiences. I strive to communicate clearly and guide teams to
            ensure user needs are always the priority.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>2021 - 2023:</strong> Freelance Designer - Branding, Website Design, and Social Media Management
            </li>
            <li><strong>2018 - 2023:</strong> Facilitator at Colegiatura - Teaching, Mentorship, and Workshops</li>
            <li>
              <strong>2017 - 2021:</strong> Designer at Trusty To You - UI/UX, Branding, Social Media Management, and Digital
              Marketing
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>2015 - 2016:</strong> Project Coordinator at Conker - Client, Designer, and Programmer Liaison
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>2013 - 2015:</strong> Administrator at Tienda Plasma - Personnel Management, Design Product Supervision,
              Administrative and Accounting Management
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>2009 - 2013:</strong> Design and Production Assistant at Plasma - Supervision and Management of Graphic
              and Industrial Clients
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Besides being a graphic designer, I have a background in psychology, complementing my user-centered design
            approach. Over five years, I have been a university lecturer in personal development, which has allowed me
            to develop assertive communication and leadership skills. These experiences enable me to approach design
            holistically, ensuring each project is empathetic, creative, and accessible.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>2024:</strong> User Experience Design (UX) - Google Coursera</li>
            <li><strong>2023:</strong> Basic UI Concepts - Platzi</li>
            <li><strong>2022 - 2023:</strong> General English Program - ILSC</li>
            <li>
