            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>2017 - 2017</strong>
              <br />
              Systemic Development Facilitation - Colegiatura
              <br />
              Assertive communication, collaborative work, critical and analytical thinking, human behavior comprehension.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>2017 - 2017</strong>
              <br />
              The Artist as a Brand - UPB
              <br />
              Web design, marketing, research and analysis, user-centered design, collaborative work.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>2014 - 2014</strong>
              <br />
              Leadership Master - Colegiatura
              <br />
              Leadership, teamwork, empathy, personal development, assertive communication.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>2005 - 2009</strong>
              <br />
              Graphic Communication - Uniminuto
              <br />
              Web design, graphic design, communication, product development.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <h3>UI Design</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Wireframe Creation, Mockups, and Prototypes (High and Low Fidelity)</li>
            <li>Responsive and Adaptive Design</li>
            <li>Design Systems</li>
          </ul>

